1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:04,970
[Fated Hearts – An Elopement Easily Stopped]

2
00:00:04,990 --> 00:00:07,510
[On-set of "Fated Hearts"]

3
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:06,200
All right, up.

4
00:00:07,580 --> 00:00:09,830
[Lifted high on wires]

5
00:00:12,250 --> 00:00:13,470
[Lands safely]

6
00:00:13,530 --> 00:00:14,430
Your Highness.

7
00:00:13,650 --> 00:00:16,050
[Tense standoff at the foot of the mountain]

8
00:00:14,430 --> 00:00:16,400
Don't hurt my brother!

9
00:00:16,270 --> 00:00:17,220
[Arrows released simultaneously]

10
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,410
One, two—release!

11
00:00:17,410 --> 00:00:18,030
[Successfully dodges]

12
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:19,660
Brother!

13
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:21,700
You're my only family.

14
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:22,730
Please let us go.

15
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:24,180
Everyone—

16
00:00:24,250 --> 00:00:25,200
retreat!

17
00:00:24,390 --> 00:00:25,330
[They choose to withdraw]

18
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:26,500
[Radiating authority]

19
00:00:25,650 --> 00:00:26,650
Stop right there!

20
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:29,090
[Completely frozen]

21
00:00:31,350 --> 00:00:32,619
Go on, keep moving!

22
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:33,040
Cut!

23
00:00:33,770 --> 00:00:35,480
[All stunned by Suige's aura]

24
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:39,330
[Can't resist mimicking]

25
00:00:38,010 --> 00:00:38,670
Stop right there!

26
00:00:38,670 --> 00:00:39,530
They're still—

27
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,190
It's raining.

28
00:00:41,460 --> 00:00:42,350
[Casting a spell]

29
00:00:42,460 --> 00:00:43,030
Freeze.

30
00:00:43,260 --> 00:00:44,750
[The rain grows heavier]

31
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:45,500
It's raining harder now.

32
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:49,230
[Draws the sword with effortless grace]

33
00:00:49,270 --> 00:00:50,330
Once he comes down,

34
00:00:51,270 --> 00:00:52,470
you can say that line—

35
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:54,600
"Don't hurt my  brother."

36
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,730
You dare come again?

37
00:00:56,700 --> 00:00:57,700
Brother—

38
00:00:57,700 --> 00:00:59,360
you're my only family.

39
00:00:59,230 --> 00:01:01,140
[Voice filled with emotion]

40
00:00:59,930 --> 00:01:01,260
Don't push me any further.

41
00:01:01,260 --> 00:01:02,400
Don't hurt my royal brother!

42
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:03,010
[Xiyang's impression show]

43
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,590
Don't hurt the Prince!
